<text><![CDATA[<b>Summary advertisements:</b><ul><li>Are sent every 5 minutes by a VTP Server</li><li>Inform VTP enabled switches of the current VTP configuration revision number</li><li>Are sent immediately after a configuration change </li></ul>]]></text>
</component>

<component id="ID_txt05">
<text><![CDATA[<b>Changes that trigger the subset advertisement include:<ul><li>Creating or deleting a VLAN</li><li>Suspending or activating a VLAN</li><li>Changing the name of a VLAN</li><li>Changing the MTU of a VLAN</li></ul></b>]]></text>
</component>

